#: data/io.github.libredeb.vinyl.metainfo.xml.in:12
msgid ""
"A desktop music player that provides a beautiful, fullscreen interface to "
"your music library. Built for those who appreciate a clean aesthetic and "
"intuitive control."
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.libredeb.vinyl.metainfo.xml.in:17
msgid ""
"Whether you prefer using your keyboard or a gamepad, Vinyl offers a seamless "
"way to navigate your tunes without ever needing to reach for a mouse. We "
"created Vinyl for music lovers who want to truly connect with their music, "
"bringing back the intentionality of listening to a record."
msgstr ""

